  <section id="availability">
    <title>Availability</title>
    <para>The source code of this card is available via the <ulink
    url="http://svn.debian.org/">Debian Subversion server</ulink> in
    DocBook/XML format.  You may access the repository via the <ulink
    url="http://svn.debian.org/wsvn/ddp/refcard/">web
    interface</ulink>.  Or check out the latest version using the
    commands:</para>

    <programlisting>svn checkout svn://svn.debian.org/svn/ddp/refcard/trunk</programlisting>

